---

---

<section
    class="med-section med-section-local"
>
    <div class="med-absolute med-inset-0 med-pointer-events-none med-opacity-20">
        <svg class="med-w-full med-h-full">
            <filter id="scratches">
                <feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.8" numOctaves="3"></feTurbulence>
                <feColorMatrix type="saturate" values="0"></feColorMatrix>
            </filter>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#404040" filter="url(#scratches)"></rect>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="med-container">
        <div class="med-grid med-grid--reverse">
            <div class="med-info-column">
                <span
                    class="med-tag med-tag-local"
                    >¿Quién Raya a Quién?</span
                >
                <h2 class="med-title med-title-local">La Escala de Mohs</h2>

                <p class="med-description med-description-local">
                    No puedes medir la dureza apretando. Tienes que destruir. Friedrich Mohs
                    organizó el mundo mineral en una pelea de patio de colegio.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="med-card med-card-local"
                >
                    <h3 class="med-card-title med-card-title-local">Del Talco al Diamante</h3>
                    <p class="med-card-text med-card-text-local">
                        Si A raya a B, A es más duro. Simple. Tu uña (2.5) raya el yeso (2). El
                        cuarzo (7) raya el vidrio (5.5).
                    </p>
                    <p class="med-card-note med-card-note-local">
                        El diamante (10) era el rey invicto, hasta que empezamos a crear materiales
                        que ni la naturaleza imaginó.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="med-visual-column med-visual-column-local">
                <div class="med-visual-wrapper">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" class="med-w-full med-h-full med-overflow-visible">
                        <rect
                            x="50"
                            y="100"
                            width="300"
                            height="150"
                            fill="#525252"
                            stroke="#737373"
                            stroke-width="2"></rect>
                        <text x="200" y="280" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a3a3a3"
                            >MUESTRA (DUREZA 5)</text
                        >

                        <path
                            d="M 60 120 L 150 140"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#262626"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.5"></path>
                        <path
                            d="M 70 200 L 120 180"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#262626"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            opacity="0.5"></path>

                        <g class="animate-scratch-move">
                            <rect x="-5" y="-60" width="10" height="60" fill="#a3a3a3"></rect>

                            <path d="M 0 0 L -5 -10 L 5 -10 Z" fill="#bbf7d0"></path>

                            <circle
                                cx="0"
                                cy="0"
                                r="15"
                                fill="white"
                                opacity="0"
                                class="animate-scratch-spark"></circle>
                        </g>

                        <path
                            d="M 100 150 L 300 150"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#e5e5e5"
                            stroke-width="3"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-dasharray="200"
                            stroke-dashoffset="200"
                            class="animate-draw-scratch"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .med-section-local {
        background-color: #262626;
        color: #e5e5e5;
    }

    .med-tag-local {
        color: #a3a3a3;
        border-color: #525252;
    }

    .med-title-local {
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .med-description-local {
        color: #d4d4d4;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .med-card-title-local {
        color: #e5e5e5;
    }

    .med-card-text-local {
        color: #a3a3a3;
    }

    .med-card-note-local {
        color: #d4d4d4;
    }

    .med-visual-column-local {
        height: 400px;
    }

    .med-card-local {
        background-color: color-mix(in srgb, #171717 50%, transparent);
        border-color: #404040;
    }

    @keyframes scratchMove {
        0% {
            transform: translate(100px, 150px) rotate(-10deg);
        }
        50% {
            transform: translate(300px, 150px) rotate(-10deg);
        }
        100% {
            transform: translate(300px, 150px) rotate(-10deg);
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }
    .animate-scratch-move {
        animation: scratchMove 2s ease-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes drawScratch {
        0% {
            stroke-dashoffset: 200;
        }
        50% {
            stroke-dashoffset: 0;
        }
        100% {
            stroke-dashoffset: 0;
        }
    }
    .animate-draw-scratch {
        animation: drawScratch 2s ease-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes scratchSpark {
        0%,
        10% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.5);
        }
        25% {
            opacity: 0.8;
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }
        50% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.5);
        }
    }
    .animate-scratch-spark {
        animation: scratchSpark 2s ease-out infinite;
    }
</style>
